casebody.data:
COMMUNITY GARAGE INC., Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
AUTO-OWNERS INSURANCE COMPANY, Defendant-Appellee. SC: 158170
COA: 339300 Supreme Court of Michigan. December 21, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the June 19, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
